ðŸ”¹ Production Safety Clarification

Currently, production is still running on the existing HTTP CRM target server URL.

The HTTPS changes were deployed using a new UDeploy component and new pipeline, completely isolated from the current production setup.

The Apigee target server URL has not been switched to HTTPS yet. Therefore:
	â€¢	No impact to existing production traffic
	â€¢	No routing changes
	â€¢	No RF or rollback impact
	â€¢	No effect on current HTTP version

This deployment only prepares the HTTPS Autosys jobs and keeps the existing PROD flow untouched.

