ðŸ”¹ Closing Statement

This approach aligns with platform security and governance standards, resolves permission-related execution failures, and ensures zero impact to the current production environment.

We are deploying the CRM Olympus HTTPS Autosys JIL files (START and STOP jobs) through the CRM Autosys repository. These jobs invoke the enterprise olympus_jobLauncher.ksh script and follow standard scheduling, logging, and retry configurations. DA5 and QA5 validation has been completed successfully. This deployment only introduces HTTPS job configuration and does not impact the current HTTP production setup.
